languages.text: "Не стоит об этом переживать — после того шума, который мы тут устроили, вряд ли кто-то сунется к контейнерам. Впрочем, мне бесконечно приятно ваше беспокойство о моей... теперь уже нашей собственности!"

traits.locale_text: "Не стоит об этом переживать — после того шума, который мы тут устроили, вряд ли кто-то сунется к контейнерам. Впрочем, мне бесконечно приятно ваше беспокойство о моей собственности!"

languages.text: "Nothing to worry about — after all the ruckus we've caused here, I doubt anyone will go anywhere near the containers. I am, however, infinitely flattered by your concern for my — now our — property!"

languages.text: “没什么好担心的，我们在这里引起了这么大的骚动，恐怕没人再敢来碰这些箱子了。不过，你这么关心我的——当然，现在已经是‘我们的’财产，我对此感到受宠若惊！”
languages.original_text: "Nothing to worry about — after all the ruckus we've caused here, I doubt anyone will go anywhere near the containers. I am, however, infinitely flattered by your concern for my — now our — property!"

traits.locale_text: “没什么好担心的，咱们在这里引起了这么大的骚动，我看恐怕没人敢来碰这些箱子。不过，你这么关心我的财产，我对此感到无比受宠若惊！”

languages.text: «No hay nada de qué preocuparse. Después de todos los problemas que hemos causado, dudo mucho que nadie se acerque a los contenedores. Por lo que a mí respecta, me halaga enormemente que te preocupes tanto por mis pertenencias... ¡ahora nuestras!».
languages.original_text: "Nothing to worry about — after all the ruckus we've caused here, I doubt anyone will go anywhere near the containers. I am, however, infinitely flattered by your concern for my — now our — property!"

traits.locale_text: «No hay nada de qué preocuparse. Después de todos los problemas que hemos causado, dudo mucho que nadie se acerque a los contenedores. Por lo que a mí respecta, ¡me halaga enormemente que te preocupes tanto por mis pertenencias!».

languages.text: 「心配ないよ…ここであれだけの騒動を起こしたんだ、誰もコンテナに近づかないさ。だけど、あたしの財産を心配してくれてとても嬉しいよ！いや、もうふたりの財産だね」
languages.original_text: "Nothing to worry about — after all the ruckus we've caused here, I doubt anyone will go anywhere near the containers. I am, however, infinitely flattered by your concern for my — now our — property!"

traits.locale_text: 「心配ないよ…ここであれだけの騒動を起こしたんだ、誰もコンテナに近づかないさ。だけど、あたしの財産を心配してくれてとても嬉しいよ！いや、もうふたりの財産だね」

languages.text: "Kein Grund zur Sorge – nach dem Chaos, das wir hier verursacht haben, wird sich den Containern bestimmt niemand nähern. Ich hingegen fühle mich wegen Eurer Bedenken bezüglich meines – und mittlerweile unseres – Eigentums sehr geschmeichelt!"
languages.original_text: "Nothing to worry about — after all the ruckus we've caused here, I doubt anyone will go anywhere near the containers. I am, however, infinitely flattered by your concern for my — now our — property!"

traits.locale_text: "Keine Sorge – nach all dem Tumult hier wird sich den Containern bestimmt niemand nähern. Ich hingegen fühle mich wegen Eurer Bedenken bezüglich meines Eigentums sehr geschmeichelt!"

languages.text: « Oh, pas d'inquiétude : après tout le tapage qu'on a provoqué, ça m'étonnerait que quelqu'un ose s'approcher des conteneurs. Mais je suis très flattée que vous vous fassiez du souci pour ma... ou plutôt notre propriété ! »
languages.original_text: "Nothing to worry about — after all the ruckus we've caused here, I doubt anyone will go anywhere near the containers. I am, however, infinitely flattered by your concern for my — now our — property!"

languages.text: "Endişelenecek bir şey yok. Yarattığımız kargaşadan sonra konteynerlerin yanına yaklaşan olacağını sanmam. Ancak malım, yani malımız hakkında endişelenmene fevkalade sevindim!"
languages.original_text: "Nothing to worry about — after all the ruckus we've caused here, I doubt anyone will go anywhere near the containers. I am, however, infinitely flattered by your concern for my — now our — property!"
